-- French Culture Ministry Opposes Wealth Tax on Art, Belkacem Says
-- B y   G r e g o r y   V i s c u s i
-- 2012-10-10T10:55:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-10/french-culture-ministry-opposes-wealth-tax-on-art-belkacem-says.html
French Culture Minister Aurelie
Filipetti told today’s cabinet meeting that she opposes a
parliamentary amendment to include artworks in calculating
 France ’s wealth tax, government spokeswoman Najat Vallaud-
Belkacem told reporters today in Paris.  “The culture minister expressed her opposition but this is
a question to be worked out in parliamentary debate,” Vallaud-
Belkacem said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Viscusi at 
